-------------------------
Installation instructions
-------------------------

1. Requirements
---------------

UploadHelper depends on the following libraries:
- wxWidgets 2.8.7 or greater
- libcurl

To compile UploadHelper 4, the following tools need to be installed:
- GCC
- GNU make
- GNU gettext

Optional tools:
- recent automake, autoconf if you plan to change configure.in or any of the
  Makefile.am files


2. Compilation
--------------

Assuming you are in the top source directory, execute the following commands:

./configure
make
make install

